    <metadata>
      <schema>http://ltsc.ieee.org/xsd/LOM</schema>
      <lom xsi:schemaLocation="http://ltsc.ieee.org/xsd/LOM http://ltsc.ieee.org/xsd/lomv1.0/lomLoose.xsd" xmlns="http://ltsc.ieee.org/xsd/LOM">
        <general>
          <identifier>
            <catalog>oercommons.org</catalog>
            <entry>1770207120</entry>
          </identifier>
          <title>
            <string language="en">The Branding of America</string>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Das Einbrennen von Amerika</string>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">Stigmatiser de l'Amérique</string>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">Marcar de América</string>
            <string language="x-mt-it">Marcare a caldo dell'America</string>
            <string language="x-mt-el">Το μαρκάρισμα της Αμερικής</string>
            <string language="x-mt-es">El calificar de América</string>
          </title>
          <description>
            <string language="en">offers thumbnail histories of nearly 30 well-known brand names associated with soft drinks, potatoes, cereal, fruit, airplanes, buses, pianos, sewing machines, jeans, shoes, and other products.</string>
          </description>
          <keyword>
            <string language="en">Social Sciences</string>
          </keyword>
          <language>en</language>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-de">bietet thumbnail Geschichten von fast 30 weithin 
bekannten Markennamen an, die mit alkoholfreien Getränken, 
Kartoffeln, Getreide, Frucht, Flugzeugen, Bussen, Klavieren, 
Nähmaschinen, Jeans, Schuhen und anderen Produkten verbunden sind.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">offre des histoires d'ongle du pouce de presque 30 
noms de marque bien connus liés aux boissons non alcooliques, aux 
pommes de terre, à la céréale, au fruit, aux avions, aux bus, aux 
pianos, aux machines à coudre, aux jeans, aux chaussures, et à 
d'autres produits.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">oferece histories do thumbnail de quase 30 nomes 
de tipo well-known associados com as bebidas macias, as batatas, o 
cereal, a fruta, os aviões, as barras-ônibus, os pianos, as 
máquinas sewing, as calças de brim, as sapatas, e os outros 
produtos.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-it">offre i dati storici del thumbnail di quasi 30 
marche ben note connesse con le bibite analcoliche, le patate, il 
cereale, la frutta, gli aeroplani, i bus, i piani, le macchine per 
cucire, i jeans, i pattini ed altri prodotti.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-el">προσφέρει τις ιστορίες νυχιών του αντίχειρα σχεδόν 
30 γνωστών εμπορικών σημάτων που συνδέονται με τα μη 
αλκοολούχα ποτά, τις πατάτες, τα δημητριακά, τα φρούτα, τα 
αεροπλάνα, τους διαδρόμους, τα πιάνα, τις ράβοντας μηχανές, τα 
τζιν, τα παπούτσια, και άλλα προϊόντα.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-es">ofrece historias del thumbnail de casi 30 marcas 
bien conocidas asociadas a las bebidas suaves, a las patatas, al 
cereal, a la fruta, a los aeroplanos, a los megabuses, a los pianos, a
las máquinas de costura, a los pantalones vaqueros, a los zapatos, y 
a otros productos.</string>
          </description>
          <keyword>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Sozialwissenschaften</string>
          </keyword>
          <keyword>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">Les Sciences Sociales</string>
          </keyword>
          <keyword>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">Ciências Sociais</string>
          </keyword>
          <keyword>
            <string language="x-mt-it">Scienze Sociali</string>
          </keyword>
          <keyword>
            <string language="x-mt-el">Κοινωνικές επιστήμες</string>
          </keyword>
          <keyword>
            <string language="x-mt-es">Ciencias Sociales</string>
          </keyword>
